Usage: saveWhatIfConstraints [-help] [<blackBoxCellName>] [-dir <dirName>]
                             [-filePrefix <prefix>] [-pt  | -dc ]

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
<blackBoxCellName>     # name of the blackbox or blackblob cell
                       # (string, optional)
-dc                    # Specifies constraint format as dc (bool, optional)
-dir <dirName>         # directory name (string, optional)
-filePrefix <prefix>   # Specifies the prefix for the constraints file name
                       # (string, optional)
-pt                    # Specifies constraint format as pt (bool, optional)